          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-11-08T22:12:20Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[This bill provides that the state approving agency for a multi-state non-federal apprenticeship program is: (1) for program approval purposes, the state approving agency for the state in which the headquarters of the apprenticeship program is located; and (2) for all other purposes, the state approving agency for the state in which the apprenticeship program takes place.  </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-10-05T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
